<li>DO NOT meet the buyer in at night or dark place - always meet in open or public area.</li>
<li>&nbsp;DO NOT meet the buyer alone. Always have someone with you and where possible meet in a public area.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Tips for Buyers</strong></p>
<ul>
