<li>Be careful of scammers - Always meet the seller</li>
<li>Ensure all documents are handed to you after sales.</li>
<li>DO NOT meet the seller at night or dark place - always meet in open or public area.</li>
<li>Never send money for a vehicle or part you haven't seen or received.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong><strong>Important notices to be aware of</strong></p>
<p>We advertise vehicles or parts/accessories on our website but we don't own, buy or sell any of the vehicles advertised on our website.</p>
<p>AutoTitanic don't provide or recommend any payment services or get involved in transactions between buyers and sellers.</p>
